OL,6,FA woman has been jailed for life for
OL,7,Fmurdering her disabled mother-in-law
OL,8,Fby setting fire to her bed while she
OL,9,Fslept.
OL,11,FElizabeth Vamplew, 77, known to her
OL,12,Ffamily as Anne, was deaf and unable to
OL,13,Fwalk unaided.
OL,15,FShe died of burns and smoke inhalation
OL,16,Fin the fire at her bungalow in on 15
OL,17,FDecember 2021.
