OL,6,Fheard Karen Vamplew, 44, was in more
OL,7,Fthan #10,000 of debt and had started
OL,8,Fthe blaze in the early hours of the
OL,9,Fmorning with the intention of killing
OL,10,Fher mother-in-law to gain inheritance
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,FVamplew disabled the location function
OL,14,Fon her phone and was caught on CCTV
OL,15,Fmaking her way to Elizabeth Vamplew's
OL,16,Fhouse on Eton Court, where she lit the
OL,17,Fbottom corner of the bed in which she
OL,18,Fwas sleeping.
