OL,6,FProsecutor Peter Joyce KC said: "The
OL,7,Fready source of cash for the defendant
OL,8,Fhad ceased and she (the victim) was no
OL,9,Flonger of use to the defendant; only a
OL,10,Fburden.
OL,12,F"The defendant did however know that
OL,13,Funder the terms of the deceased's will
OL,14,Fthe defendant's husband stood to
OL,15,Finherit half his mother's estate. The
OL,16,Fwill was later found at her home."
