OL,6,FThe court heard Vamplew returned to
OL,7,Fthe scene of the fire later in the
OL,8,Fmorning, now dressed in pyjamas, and
OL,9,Fattempted to make it look like
OL,10,FElizabeth had summoned her in distress
OL,11,Fthrough a lifeline system she wore on
OL,12,Fa pendant.
OL,14,FDet Ch Insp Clare Dean from
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police said:
OL,16,F"Throughout this investigation Vamplew
OL,17,Fmaintained that she was not
OL,18,Fresponsible for the death of her own
OL,19,Fmother-in-law.
