OL,6,F"The simple fact is that she
OL,7,Fdeliberately set a catastrophic and
OL,8,Ffatal fire knowing full well that
OL,9,FElizabeth was asleep inside the
OL,10,Fproperty. It was a brutal and
OL,11,Fpremeditated act borne out of
OL,12,Fwickedness and greed."
OL,14,FIn a statement Elizabeth's family
OL,15,Fdescribed her as a "devoted mother,
OL,16,Fsister, grandmother, aunt, and friend
OL,17,Fto many" who will be "greatly missed
OL,18,Fby her family and many friends".
OL,20,FKaren Vamplew was sentenced to life
OL,21,Fwith a minimum term of 32 years.
